  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed development due to its overall size, scale and its siting directly adjacent to the public highway would be overly prominent, overbearing and intrusive resulting in a detrimental impact to the character and appearance of the original building and the surrounding area. The proposed development is contrary to the high quality design aspirations of The National Planning Policy Framework (2021), policy D3.D(1) and D3.D(11) of The London Plan (2021), policy CS1.B of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012) and policy DM1 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed development would result in the loss of the existing front forecourt which is capable of being use for servicing and deliveries and the applicant has failed to demonstrate to the satisfaction of the Local Planning Authority how the property would be serviced. The proposed development is therefore contrary to the National Planning Policy Framework (2021), policy T7 of The London Plan (2021), policy DM1.B(f) and policy DM44.A of The Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan 2013. "
